據[[2001年英國人口普查|2001年英國人口普查]]顯示，柯科迪的常住人口為46912人，佔法夫郡總人口的13.4% 。<ref name="Kdy population">{{Cite web|title=Comparative Population: Kirkcaldy Locality Scotland|url=http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Population&mainArea=Kirkcaldy&mainLevel=Locality|accessdate=2008-10-30|author=|date=|year=2001|format=|publisher=scrol.co.uk|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223141554/http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Population&mainArea=Kirkcaldy&mainLevel=Locality|archivedate=2012-02-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>報告亦指出共有21365戶家庭居於柯科迪，14.8%為[[同居|同居]]已婚夫婦，16.4%為單身家庭，18.8% 為同居未婚夫婦，7.9% 為空巢家庭。<ref name="Kdy Household">{{Cite web|title=Comparative Household Profile: Kirkcaldy Locality Scotland|url=http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Household&mainLevel=Locality&mainText=Kirkcaldy&mainTextExplicitMatch=false&compLevel=CountryProfile&compText=&compTextExplicitMatch=null|accessdate=2011-09-17|author=|date=|year=2001|format=|publisher=scrol.gov.uk|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101082638/http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Household&mainLevel=Locality&mainText=Kirkcaldy&mainTextExplicitMatch=false&compLevel=CountryProfile&compText=&compTextExplicitMatch=null|archive-date=2013-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年，柯科迪的人口數目稍微下跌至49560人。<ref name="Population Estimates">{{Cite web|title=Mid-2010 Population Estimates – Localities in order of size|url=http://www.gro-scotland.gov.uk/files2/stats/population-estimates/special-area/settlements-localities2010/2010-localities-table2.pdf|accessdate=2012-11-25|year=2012|publisher=General Register for Scotland|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031042339/http://www.gro-scotland.gov.uk/files2/stats/population-estimates/special-area/settlements-localities2010/2010-localities-table2.pdf|archive-date=2012-10-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2011年英國人口普查顯示，人口數字已經增加到49,709人。<ref name="GROS 2012 Table 3a">{{Cite web|title=Estimated population of localities by broad age groups, mid-2012|url=https://www.nrscotland.gov.uk/files//statistics/population-estimates/special-area/mid-2012-settlements/2012-pop-est-sett-local-main-tab3a.pdf|accessdate=2018-10-05|date=2012|publisher=General Register Office for Scotland|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204064501/https://www.nrscotland.gov.uk/files//statistics/population-estimates/special-area/mid-2012-settlements/2012-pop-est-sett-local-main-tab3a.pdf|archive-date=2019-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年全柯科迪地區總人口估計為59784人，預計至2026年人口將增加18% 。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Area Local Strategic Assessment">{{Cite web|title=Draft Kirkcaldy Area Local Strategic Assessment 2016|url=http://publications.fifedirect.org.uk/c64_Kirkcaldy_LSA_DRAFT.pdf|accessdate=2017-08-11|format=[[Portable_Document_File|PDF]]|publisher=Fife Council Research Team|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811143506/http://publications.fifedirect.org.uk/c64_Kirkcaldy_LSA_DRAFT.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kirkcaldy Area General Profile">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Area General Profile|url=http://knowfife.fife.gov.uk/IAS/profiles/profile?profileId=1&geoTypeId=141&geoIds=AREAD|accessdate=2013-10-25|publisher=knowfife.fife.gov.uk}}</ref>2016年，共有29246戶家庭居於柯科迪，其中67% 購入自住房屋，27%居民租住公共房屋，5%租住私人房屋。 36%居民獨居，16.1%的居民處於低收入水平。柯科迪每周平均收入為335英鎊。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Area Local Strategic Assessment" />

96.52% 居民在英國出生（其中87.15% 在蘇格蘭出生），0.28%在[[爱尔兰|愛爾蘭共和國]]出生，1.18%來自其他[[欧洲联盟|歐盟]]國家，1.86%來自世界其他地方。<ref name="Kdy population" />16-74歲居中，40.13%擔任全職工作 ，當中12.17%擔任兼職工作，4.79%是自僱人士，5.68%正處於失業狀態。有工作的學生佔2.57% ，無工作的學生佔3.06% ，退休人仕佔15.70% ，家庭主婦／夫佔5.51% ，長期病患和傷殘人士共佔佔6.68% ，因其他原因不從事經濟活動者佔3.71% 。<ref name="KdyEmployment">{{Cite web|title=Comparative Employment Profile: Kirkcaldy Locality Scotland|url=http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Employment&mainLevel=Locality&mainText=Kirkcaldy&mainTextExplicitMatch=false&compLevel=CountryProfile&compText=&compTextExplicitMatch=null|accessdate=2008-09-30|author=|date=|year=2001|format=|publisher=scrol.gov.uk|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223141712/http://www.scrol.gov.uk/scrol/browser/profile.jsp?profile=Employment&mainLevel=Locality&mainText=Kirkcaldy&mainTextExplicitMatch=false&compLevel=CountryProfile&compText=&compTextExplicitMatch=null|archive-date=2012-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>與蘇格蘭其他地方相比，柯科迪整體移民比例較低，但75歲以上的移民比例較高。<ref name="Kdy population" />

2010年，柯科迪地區有超過7000人申請失業救濟，比2009年減少了約90人，但比[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|金融海嘯]]前增加了500人。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Economic Profile8">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile|url=http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|accessdate=2012-05-08|author=|date=December 2011|format=|publisher=Fife Council|pages=8|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184838/http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>最近一次{{Link-en|蘇格蘭多重剝奪指數|Scottish Index of Multiple Deprivation}}數據顯示，法夫最貧困的地區是加拉頓和排名82的辛加敦，此兩地均處於蘇格蘭最貧困地區的5% 。柯科迪的林克敦、西菲爾德、海菲爾德、斯米頓和坦普霍爾東部地區均處於蘇格蘭最貧困社區的5-10% 。<ref name="SIMD Indicators">{{Cite web|title=Local Authority Summary- SIMD 2012– Fife|url=http://www.scotland.gov.uk/Resource/0041/00410730.pdf|accessdate=2013-01-11|author=|date=|format=[[Portable_Document_File|PDF]]|work=simd.scotland.gov.uk|publisher=|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202121020/http://www.scotland.gov.uk/Resource/0041/00410730.pdf|archive-date=2013-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

