== 經濟 ==
該鎮最早發展的工業是煤礦開採和淘鹽，自十六世紀早期開始發展。<ref name="Torrie and Coleman15–19"/>柯科迪和鄰近的柏夫赫是早期生產粗布和釘子的重鎮，而柯科迪製造的釘子被用於17世紀[[荷里路德宮|荷里路德宮]]的修復工程上。<ref name="Torrie and Coleman15–19" />柯科迪的亞麻織造業始於1672年，且對這個小鎮愈加重要。亞麻織造廠所使用的紗線由[[汉堡|汉堡]]和[[不来梅|不来梅]]進口。<ref name="Glen120">Glen 2007, p.120.</ref>

柯科迪的製陶業始於1714年，製陶工場聚集於連頓、 加拉頓和辛加敦一帶。<ref name="Glen158">Glen 2007, p.158.</ref>由安德魯和阿奇伯·格雷（Andrew and Archibald Gray）於1817年創立的法夫陶器廠生產了以維米斯家族命名的維米斯陶器。<ref name="Glen161">Glen 2007, p.161.</ref>

1828年，米高·乃因（Michael Nairn）成立一家生產重帆布的小工廠。<ref name="Smith287–288">Smith 1952, pp.287–288.</ref>乃因受[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托爾]]的工廠啟發，遂從{{Link-en|腓特烈·禾頓|Frederick Walton}}獲得的地板布專利權，並於1847年開始在自己位於柏夫赫的新工廠生產地板布，並開始使用焗爐烘乾地板布，減少生產時間。<ref name="Glen140">Glen 2007, p.140.</ref>專利權過期後，乃因在1877年轉而生產[[油毡|油氈]]。<ref name="Glen142">Glen 2007, p.142.</ref>曾經為米高·乃因工作的工人亦紛紛建立工廠，生產地板布和油氈。<ref name="Smith287–288" />

大約有22200人在柯科迪地區工作，其中大部分人於柯科迪就業，少部分人到{{Link-en|本泰蘭|Burntisland}}工作。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile5–6">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile|url=http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|accessdate=2012-05-08|author=|date=December 2011|format=|publisher=Fife Council|pages=5–6|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184838/http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>柯科迪地區職位數目佔法夫郡職位數量的13.6%。<ref name="Fife Economic Strategy p6">{{Cite web|title=Fife Economic Strategy 2013-2023|url=https://www.fva.org/downloads/Fife_Economic_Strategy_2013_2023.pdf|accessdate=2019-07-19|author=|date=2013-10-01|format=[[Portable_Document_File|PDF]]|publisher=Fife Economy Partnership|pages=6|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719151147/https://www.fva.org/downloads/Fife_Economic_Strategy_2013_2023.pdf|archive-date=2019-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>服務業是柯科迪地區的最重要產業。零售業和建築業亦為柯科迪地區的重要經濟支柱，金融和商業服務業的就業機會較少。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile5–6" />MGt電訊是柯科迪最大規模的公司。<ref>{{Cite web|title=65 jobs go at Kirkcaldy call centre|url=https://www.fifetoday.co.uk/news/65-jobs-go-at-kirkcaldy-call-centre-1-160088|accessdate=2019-07-21|work=www.fifetoday.co.uk|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721145259/https://www.fifetoday.co.uk/news/65-jobs-go-at-kirkcaldy-call-centre-1-160088|archive-date=2019-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>其他大規模的本地公司包括{{Link-en|法夫國民保健署|NHS Fife}}、製造乙烯基地毯的科寶公司 、法夫學院、威禾夫控股麵粉廠（Whitworths Holdings）和史密夫安達臣造紙廠（Smith Anderson）。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile14–15">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile|url=http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|accessdate=2012-05-08|author=|date=December 2011|format=|publisher=Fife Council|pages=14–15|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184838/http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

柯科迪主要的工業和商業區包括米治萊頓（Mitchleston）、倫道夫、希菲和約翰·史密斯商業園。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile3">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Area Economic Profile|url=http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|accessdate=2012-05-08|author=|date=December 2011|format=|publisher=Fife Council|pages=3|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184838/http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_Kirkcaldy_EconProfile.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨著2011年柯科迪港重新開放予貨船，當地的工業活動也有所增加。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Harbour to re-open"/>卡爾麵粉廠（Carr's Flour Mills）、福思港口（Forth Port）和蘇格蘭運輸公司之間的合作促進柯科迪港的重新開放。福思港口提供了超過80萬英鎊的貨運設施補助金來興建新的信息煙囪和傳送系統，使船運更快速。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Harbour to re-open" />

柯科迪市中心是柯科迪約13萬居民的聚集之處，居民只需花20分鐘便可到達市中心。柯科迪亦擁有法夫郡最大規模的購物中心。<ref name="KDY Town Centre Factsheet">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Town Centre Fact Sheet|url=http://www.fife.gov.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_KirkcaldyTownCentreFS.pdf|accessdate=2011-06-17|date=October 2006|format=PDF|publisher=Fife Council}}</ref>2010年，法夫議會計劃為柯科迪市中心設立{{Link-en|商業改善區|Business improvement district#United Kingdom}}，獲得當地企業投票支持。<ref name="Kirkcaldy BID">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy wins YES vote for town centre Business Improvement District|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/news/index.cfm?fuseaction=news.display&objectid=2F4993F5-95AA-6A6C-85757AE1A9D2B7F0|accessdate=2011-06-17|author=|date=2010-03-05|format=|publisher=Fife Council|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609122931/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/news/index.cfm?fuseaction=news.display&objectid=2F4993F5-95AA-6A6C-85757AE1A9D2B7F0|archive-date=2011-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>大街與濱海中心（Esplanade）平行，沿路有墟市購物中心（Mercat Shopping Centre）和布斯廷購物中心（Posting Shopping Centre）。大街的外觀改善工程已於2011年年底完成。<ref name="High Street's new look">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy High Street's new look revealed!|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/news/index.cfm?fuseaction=news.display&objectid=601A37B8-F9EF-297E-B21FD94822D95A1F|accessdate=2011-11-06|author=|date=2011-11-02|format=|publisher=Fife Council|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401210616/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/news/index.cfm?fuseaction=news.display&objectid=601A37B8-F9EF-297E-B21FD94822D95A1F|archive-date=2012-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>工程完成後，「綠色走廊」將主要的火車站、公共汽車站與大街連接起來。<ref name="green corridor">{{Cite web|title=Work set to begin on Kirkcaldy's 'Green Corridor|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/yourtown/index.cfm?fuseaction=news.display&town=F4CE47C8-8E20-4229-92DF6169F7EB7E4D&objectid=26F82106-9380-C1E2-27FED72683A03DC0|accessdate=2011-06-21|date=2011-05-25|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318152845/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/yourtown/index.cfm?fuseaction=news.display&town=F4CE47C8-8E20-4229-92DF6169F7EB7E4D&objectid=26F82106-9380-C1E2-27FED72683A03DC0|archive-date=2012-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>整個項目的預算為400萬英鎊，其中200萬英鎊由隸屬於[[蘇格蘭政府|蘇格蘭政府]]的「城鎮中心重建基金」提供。<ref name="Town Centre Regeneration Fund">{{Cite web|title=Town Centre Regeneration Fund first tranche|url=http://www.scotland.gov.uk/Topics/Built-Environment/regeneration/town-centres/tcrf/FirstTrancheAllocations|accessdate=2010-04-13|date=2010-12-18|publisher=Scottish Government|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606141127/http://www.scotland.gov.uk/Topics/Built-Environment/regeneration/town-centres/tcrf/FirstTrancheAllocations|archive-date=2011-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

柯科迪露天購物中心建於1997年，位於小鎮西北部的教堂平路（鄰近A92公路），是零售商倉庫的集中地。<ref name="Fife Central Retail Park">{{Cite web|title=Fife Central Retail Park, Kirkcaldy|url=http://www.hammerson.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=133289&p=prop-pd-Fife-Central-Retail-Park|accessdate=2011-03-06|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Hammerson|language=}}</ref><ref name="Glen289–290">Glen 2007, pp.289–290.</ref>2005年4月，倫敦房地產開發商漢馬臣（Hammerson）以7500萬英鎊買下購物中心。<ref name="Glen289–290" />

==文化==
[[File:KMAG_(Kirkcaldy_Museum_and_Art_Gallery).jpg|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:KMAG_(Kirkcaldy_Museum_and_Art_Gallery).jpg]]
{{Link-en|柯科迪藝廊|Kirkcaldy Galleries}}集博物館、藝術畫廊和中央圖書館於一身。該建築物於1925年啟用，原先只用作博物館和藝術館，1928年博物館擴建為主要圖書館。<ref name="History and Celebration33">Kirkcaldy Civic Society, 2005, p.33.</ref><ref name="Remembered72">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2007, p.72.</ref>2011年，博物館閉館進行一項耗資240萬英鎊的翻新工程，2013年6月重新開放。翻新後，博物館增添一個單一的入口和接待台將建築內的設施整合在一起。這座建築物也更名為「柯科迪藝廊」。<ref name="library and museum to get revamp">{{Cite news|author=Simpson|first=Donna|title=Library and museum to get refurb – 86 years on!|publisher=''Fife Free Press''|location=Kirkcaldy|page=4|date=2011-09-29}}</ref><ref name="new name for museum">{{Cite news|author=Scoon|first=Tanya|title=I name this building...|location=Kirkcaldy|publisher=''Fife Free Press''|pages=9–10|date=2013-01-24}}</ref><ref name="museum thinking big">{{Cite news|author=Watson|first=Jonathan|title=Museum is thinking big|location=Dundee|publisher=The Courier (Fife Edition)|page=7|date=2013-02-04}}</ref>柯科迪的主要劇院為亞當 · 史密斯劇院，該處經常舉辦戲劇演出和音樂會，以及放映一系列[[藝術電影|藝術電影]]和商業電影。<ref name="History and Celebration54">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, p.54.</ref><ref name="Adam Smith Theatre">{{Cite web|title=Adam Smith Theatre – Overview|url=http://www.onfife.com/venues/adam-smith-theatre/overview|date=2011-11-23|publisher=Arts and Theatres Trust, Fife|access-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102135115/http://www.onfife.com/venues/adam-smith-theatre/overview|archive-date=2014-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>該劇院原名亞當·斯密堂，1973年為了迎接[[亚当·斯密|亞當·斯密]]誕辰250週年，劇院得以翻修，並更名為亞當 · 史密斯劇院。<ref name="History and Celebration54" />

林克斯市場起源於林克斯街的[[农贸市场|農貿市場]]，1903年搬到海濱長廊（當時稱為山市路）。<ref name="History and Celebration25–26"/><ref name="Remembered105">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2007, p.105.</ref>每年四月林克斯市場均會有大型市集，2004年正是林克斯市場成立700週年。<ref name="History and Celebration25–26" />1962年9月，柯科迪與德國的英戈爾施塔特建立了結成姐妹城市。<ref name="a list of Fife's twin towns">{{Cite web|title=Civic Affairs – Twinning and Networking|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/topics/index.cfm?fuseaction=service.display&subjectid=A2927412-C78A-11D5-909E0008C7844101&objectid=18225846-FC6E-4165-9ECDC72F0DC4BEA1|accessdate=2011-02-20|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318152416/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/topics/index.cfm?fuseaction=service.display&subjectid=A2927412-C78A-11D5-909E0008C7844101&objectid=18225846-FC6E-4165-9ECDC72F0DC4BEA1|archive-date=2012-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="50 Year Link">{{Cite news|author=Scoon|first=Tanya|title=50 Years As Twins!|publisher=''Fife Free Press''|location=Kirkcaldy|page=15|date=2011-11-17}}</ref>2012年柯科迪與英戈爾斯塔特共同舉辦一個聯合慶祝活動，紀念兩地結成姐妹城市50週年。<ref name="50 Year Link" />

柯科迪有三個主要公園，分別是貝弗域治公園（Beveridge Park）、雷文斯基格公園（Ravenscraig Park）和鄧尼克公園（Dunnikier Park）。貝弗域治公園佔地104英畝（420,000平方米），透過購買雷斯莊園土地，以及擴建羅比公園而成。<ref name="Beveridge Park">{{Cite web|title=Beveridge Park|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=ACD495D9-2942-423E-A89B2874D1E99F3A|accessdate=2011-04-07|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101141807/http://fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=ACD495D9-2942-423E-A89B2874D1E99F3A|archive-date=2011-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>公園也是亞麻製造商、教務長米高貝弗域治（Michael Beveridge，於1890年去世）總值5萬英鎊的遺產的一部分。<ref name="Beveridge Park7–9">Kirkcaldy Civic Society, 2000, p.7–9.</ref><ref name="Fife's green and pleasant land12–13">{{Cite news|author=Simpson|first=Donna|title=A Warm Welcome to Fife's green and (very) pleasant land...|publisher=''Fife Free Press''|location=Kirkcaldy|pages=12–13|date=2011-07-28}}</ref>1892年9月24日，一萬多人出席其由遺孀、教務長、地方法官和皇家自治鎮議會主持的公園開幕禮。<ref name="Fife's green and pleasant land12–13" /><ref name="Beveridge Park11">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2000, p.11.</ref>貝弗域治公園內建有划船湖泊、噴泉花園、滑板公園、橄欖球場，足球場和林地步道。<ref name="Greenspace Audit in Kirkcaldy9">{{Cite web|title=Fife Greenspace Audit – Kirkcaldy Area Committee|url=http://admin.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_KirkcaldyAreaCommittee.pdf|accessdate=2011-04-07|date=September 2009|format=PDF|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807214120/http://admin.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_KirkcaldyAreaCommittee.pdf|archive-date=2011-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>公園於2010年和2011年兩度獲得{{Link-en|綠旗獎|Green flag award}}。<ref name="Fife's green and pleasant land12–13" />雷文斯基格公園位於城鎮的東部，毗鄰{{Link-en|雷文斯基格城堡|Ravenscraig Castle}}。公園前身是戴薩莊園。<ref name="Greenspace Audit in Kirkcaldy p2">{{Cite web|title=Fife Greenspace Audit – Kirkcaldy Area Committee|url=http://admin.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_KirkcaldyAreaCommittee.pdf|accessdate=2011-04-07|date=September 2009|format=PDF|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807214120/http://admin.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_KirkcaldyAreaCommittee.pdf|archive-date=2011-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>1929年，油氈製造商米高·乃因爵士把戴薩莊園的土地捐出而成為花園。<ref name="Remembered56">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2007, p.56.</ref>鄧尼克公園位於小鎮北部，前身為建於1790年的鄧尼克宅第（國會議員{{Link-en|占士·湯臣·奧斯和|James Townsend Oswald}}曾居於此）。莊園於1945年被鎮議會買下，改建成公園。現今鄧尼克公園建有林地人行道。<ref name="Dunnikier Park">{{Cite web|title=Dunnikier Park|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=15C97B68-06AC-7E25-D904096A8867851A|accessdate=2011-04-07|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318152529/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=15C97B68-06AC-7E25-D904096A8867851A|archive-date=2012-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Omand200">Omand 2000, p.200.</ref>

== 運動與文娛 ==
[[File:San_Starko.JPG|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:San_Starko.JPG]]
[[拉夫流浪足球會|拉夫流浪足球會]]是位於柯科迪的足球會，現時於{{Link-en|蘇格蘭甲組聯賽|Scottish League One}}作賽，其主場為{{Link-en|斯塔克公園球場|Stark's Park}}。<ref name="Raith Rovers">{{Cite web|title=Raith Rovers F.C. team information|url=http://www.spfl.co.uk/clubs/raith/|accessdate=2013-08-02|publisher=Scottish Professional Football League|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130806145423/http://spfl.co.uk/clubs/raith/|archive-date=2013-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉夫流浪足球會成立於1883年，1902年進入[[蘇格蘭足球聯賽|蘇格蘭足球聯盟]]作賽。<ref name="History and Celebration50–52">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, pp.50–52.</ref><ref name="Potter and Jones286">Potter and Jones 2008, p.286.</ref>他們在1921-22賽季升班至蘇格蘭足球聯賽，以第三名完成賽季。 1937-38賽季，他們在34場比賽中攻入142球，創下了英國球隊的進球記錄。<ref name="History and Celebration50–52" /><ref name="Potter and Jones286" />在主教練{{Link-en|吉米·力高|Jimmy Nicholl}}的帶領下，球隊在1994-95賽季以甲級聯賽冠軍的身份升班至[[蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽_(1998年-2013年)|蘇格蘭超級聯賽]]。<ref name="Potter and Jones286" />1994年，拉夫流浪足球會贏得球會成立以來第一個全國冠軍，加時後雙方仍然踢成2-2平手，要[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]，最終拉夫流浪以比數6：5擊敗[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]，贏得了蘇格蘭聯賽盃，<ref name="Potter and Jones286" /><ref name="Remembered52">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2007, p.52.</ref>並能於下一季參加[[欧足联欧洲联赛|歐足聯歐洲聯賽]]，但球隊在第二輪遭[[拜仁慕尼黑足球俱乐部|拜仁慕尼黑]]淘汰。<ref name="Potter and Jones286" />

青少年足球隊{{Link-en|柯科迪和戴薩|Kirkcaldy & Dysart F.C.}}（Kirkcaldy and Dysart）亦以柯科迪為基地，其主場為丹菲公園，現時於在{{Link-en|蘇格蘭少年聯賽東部南聯賽|Scottish Junior Football East Region South Division}}作賽。<ref name="East Region League">{{Cite web|title=East Region Premier Division – Tables|url=http://www.ultrasoft2.co.uk/ersjfa/tables.asp?Competition=McBookie.com%20South%20Division&Season=2018|accessdate=2018-05-30|publisher=Scottish Junior Football Association (East Region)}}</ref>1916年解散的{{Link-en|柯科迪聯|Kirkcaldy United}}曾經以柯科迪為基地。

柯科迪皇家橄欖球隊以柯科迪為基地，在蘇格蘭國家二級聯賽中作賽，其主場位於貝弗域治公園。<ref name="History and Celebration50–52" />法夫飛人隊成立於1938年，是英國歷史最悠久的冰球隊。<ref name="Fife Flyers want silverware for 70th anniversary">{{Cite web|title=Flyers bid for first silverware of season|url=http://www.fifetoday.co.uk/sport/flyers_bid_for_first_silverware_of_season_1_151647|accessdate=2011-02-17|date=2008-10-01|publisher=The Fife Free Press (Fife Today)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315101920/http://www.fifetoday.co.uk/sport/flyers_bid_for_first_silverware_of_season_1_151647|archive-date=2012-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>這支球隊在法夫冰上體育館比賽，自2011 / 2012賽季以來一直是精英聯賽一員。<ref name="Promoting Fife: Kirkcaldy">{{Cite web|title=Promoting Fife: Kirkcaldy|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/promotingfife/downloads/Kirkcaldy_factsheet.pdf|accessdate=2011-06-21|format=PDF|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318152443/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/promotingfife/downloads/Kirkcaldy_factsheet.pdf|archive-date=2012-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Flyers to join Elite">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/ice-hockey/13903353|title=Fife Flyers will join the Elite League for next season|work=BBC Sport|date=2011-06-24|accessdate=2013-08-12}}</ref>亦有板球俱樂部和奪旗式美式足球俱樂部以柯科迪為基地，分別以鄧尼克公園和貝弗域治公園為主場。<ref name="History and Celebration50–52" /><ref name="Kirkcaldy Bulls">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Bulls Flag Football Club Statistics|url=http://www.bafacl.com/DisplayTeamNews.do?noticePlacementID=6123822&noticeID=894539&teamID=6145563&league=1015756|accessdate=2011-07-09|publisher=BAFA (British American Football Association)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323143845/http://www.bafacl.com/DisplayTeamNews.do?noticePlacementID=6123822&noticeID=894539&teamID=6145563&league=1015756|archive-date=2012-03-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，柯科迪擁有一系列休閒設施，包括游泳池、溜冰場和兩個高爾夫球場。<ref name="Promoting Fife: Kirkcaldy" />

2013年9月，位於濱海中心附近，耗資1500萬英鎊的新文娛中心開幕，以取代上世紀70年代建成的柯科迪游泳池。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Leisure Centre complete">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy - Leisure Centre|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/minisites/index.cfm?fuseaction=page.display&pageid=EAE79801-B950-BA94-817DC0A4DBE50103&siteID=F45316A8-7236-4F0E-A8B788029725EBB6|accessdate=2014-02-17|publisher=Active Fife}}</ref>新文娛中心的工程導致一個公共停車場蒙受虧損，因而引發爭議。由拯救停車場運動組織發起的請願活動收集了超過7,000個簽名，支持停車場繼續營運。<ref name="car park access rights">{{Cite web|title=Fife Council's £100,000 budget to buy car park access rights|url=http://www.fifetoday.co.uk/news/local-headlines/fife_council_s_163_100_000_budget_to_buy_car_park_access_rights_1_162028|accessdate=2011-04-15|date=2010-07-15|publisher=''Fife Free Press''|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315102137/http://www.fifetoday.co.uk/news/local-headlines/fife_council_s_163_100_000_budget_to_buy_car_park_access_rights_1_162028|archive-date=2012-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Thousands of objections">{{Cite web|title=Thousands of objections to Kirkcaldy car park closure order|url=http://www.fifetoday.co.uk/news/local-headlines/thousands_of_objections_to_kirkcaldy_car_park_closure_order_1_162875|accessdate=2010-03-18|date=2011-04-15|publisher=''Fife Free Press''|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315102145/http://www.fifetoday.co.uk/news/local-headlines/thousands_of_objections_to_kirkcaldy_car_park_closure_order_1_162875|archive-date=2012-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>該組織表示，若關閉停車場，將阻礙消化者前往商業街，店主亦會喪失停車場使用權。<ref name="car park access rights" /><ref name="Thousands of objections" />新文娛中心選址決定受到了內部審計報告的嚴厲批評。<ref name="council officials criticied for Kirkcaldy swimming pool">{{Cite web|title=Council officials criticised for over-optimism on new Kirkcaldy Swimming Pool|url=http://www.thecourier.co.uk/News/Fife/article/11894/council-officials-criticised-for-over-optimism-on-new-kirkcaldy-swimming-pool.html|accessdate=2011-04-15|date=2011-03-16|publisher=''The Courier''|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623103516/http://www.thecourier.co.uk/News/Fife/article/11894/council-officials-criticised-for-over-optimism-on-new-kirkcaldy-swimming-pool.html|archive-date=2011-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="leisure centre fiasco">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy swimming pool fiasco continues|url=http://scottishecho.co.uk/kirkcaldy-swimming-pool-fiasco-continues/#more-320|accessdate=2011-04-14|date=2011-03-14|publisher=The Scottish Echo|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110826210218/http://scottishecho.co.uk/kirkcaldy-swimming-pool-fiasco-continues/#more-320|archive-date=2011-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 地標 ==
[[File:(Square_Norman_Tower_of)_Old_Kirk,_Kirkcaldy.jpg|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:(Square_Norman_Tower_of)_Old_Kirk,_Kirkcaldy.jpg]]
老教區教堂（Old Kirk）是柯科迪最古老的教堂，位於柯克·溫德街。<ref name="Pearson16">Pearson 1993, p.16.</ref>對老教區教堂的最早記載是在1244年，時為聖安德魯斯主教{{Link-en|伯南的大衛|David de Bernham}}對聖布賴斯和[[聖博德|聖博德]]的[[祝聖|祝聖禮]]。<ref name="History and Celebration17–18" />隨著時間流逝，教堂日益失修，教堂主體大規模的翻修工程在1807年開展，至1808年完成。<ref name="Torrie and Coleman46">Torrie and Coleman 1995, p.46.</ref><ref name="Glen14">Glen 2007, p.14.</ref>重建工程後，只有建於16世紀的廣場西塔仍原封不動，它現今為老城區現存最古老的建築。<ref name="Glen14" /><ref name="Pride51–53">Pride 1998, pp.51–53.</ref>2000年，老教區教堂與聖布賴杜教堂合併，2008年停止向公眾開放。此後，老教會信託基金將教堂活化為音樂和戲劇表演場所。該鎮其他重要的教堂包括由占士·馬修斯（James Matthews）建於1881年的聖布賴杜教區教堂，坐落於聖布賴杜大道和柯克·溫德街的交界；阿布沙教區教堂則坐落阿布沙路，目前的教堂建築於1788年建成；林克敦教堂由佐治·希（George Hay）建於1830年至1881年，教堂座落於伯利恆廣場。<ref name="Glen180">Glen 2007, p.180.</ref>

{{Link-en|柯科迪鎮政廳|Kirkcaldy Town House}}立於市政廣場的中心。<ref name="Pride51–53" /><ref name="History and Celebration114">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, p.114.</ref>鎮政廳由來自愛丁堡的大衛·卡爾（David Carr）和威廉·侯活（William Howard）於1930年代末設計。<ref name="Glen261">Glen 2007, p.261.</ref>建築工程因[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]被推遲到1950年。<ref name="Glen261" />西翼和東翼分別於1953年和1956年建成。<ref name="Glen261" /><ref name="Fife Council13">Fife Council 2000, p.13.</ref>

戰爭紀念花園中的柯科迪戰爭紀念碑（Kirkcaldy War Memorial）是由米高·乃因的孫子約翰·乃因（John Nairn）豎立，以紀念死於第一次世界大戰的兒子伊恩·乃因（Ian Nairn），紀念碑於1925年揭幕。<ref name="Remembered72" /><ref name="Glen244">Glen 2007, p.244.</ref>1958年，由湯瑪斯·哈伯德（Thomas Hubbard）設計的第二次世界大戰紀念碑揭幕。<ref name="Glen244" />這兩座紀念碑是為紀念兩次世界大戰中陣亡者。<ref name="Town Centre Walkabout9">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2000, p.9.</ref>

早期商賈和船東的住所與柯科迪港口相連。<ref name="Torrie and Coleman61">Torrie and Coleman 1995, p.61.</ref>羅氏家族（Law）所居住的商賈宅邸（Merchant House）位於大街339-343號，是為具16世紀風格的蘇格蘭聯排別墅；<ref name="Pride55–58">Pride 1998, pp.55–58.</ref><ref name="Glen22">Glen 2007, p.22.</ref><ref name="Law's Close, Kirkcaldy">{{Cite web|title=Law's Close, Kirkcaldy: Project Sheet|url=http://www.shbt.org.uk/files/9513/3882/7298/laws_close_kirkcaldy-project-sheet.pdf|accessdate=2013-08-11|publisher=Scottish Historic Buildings Trust (SHBT)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061813/http://www.shbt.org.uk/files/9513/3882/7298/laws_close_kirkcaldy-project-sheet.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>海員宅邸（Sailors' Walk）位於大街443-449號，住宅由兩個17世紀的房子組成，建成年份可追溯到約1460年。<ref name="Pride55–58" /><ref name="Pride55–58" /><ref name="NTS104">National Trust for Scotland 1976, p.104.</ref>這兩所房子曾經被分成4所住宅，其中3所屬於奧理芬家族（Oliphant），第4所屬於占士·亞當·費格遜。<ref name="Glen47">Glen 2007, p.47.</ref>

海港以北的小徑樹立了兩個風格獨特的建築。<ref name="Pride55–58" />赫治臣宅邸（Hutchison's House）由附近東橋酒廠（East Bridge distillery）的老闆佐治·斯皮爾斯（George Spears）於1793年建造。<ref name="Pride55–58" /><ref name="Torrie and Coleman63–64">Torrie and Coleman 1995, pp.63–64.</ref>帕斯小屋（原名鄧尼克小屋）是約翰 · 屈臣（John Watson）於1692年為他的新娘尤凡 · 奧洛（Euphan Orrock）建造的一座三層長形平面塔式小屋。 <ref name="Torrie and Coleman63–64" /><ref name="Glen67">Glen 2007, p.67.</ref>1703年，屈臣將房子賣給與這座城市有著重要的聯繫的奧斯和家族。<ref name="Torrie and Coleman63–64" />

柯科迪有兩座宏偉的大宅。鄧尼克大宅位於柯科迪北部，建於18世紀晚期，奧斯和家族曾於這裡居住。<ref name="History and Celebration13&ndash14">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, pp.13–14.</ref>拉夫大宅在柯科迪的西南方，由第四代拉夫和梅維爾伯爵亞歷山大·拉夫爵士（Sir Alexander Raith）於17世紀末為他的新娘芭芭拉·登打士（Barbara Dundas）建造。<ref name="History and Celebration13&ndash14" /><ref name="Pride103">Pride 1998, p.103.</ref>拉夫大宅現今是是門羅-費格遜一家的私人住宅。<ref name="History and Celebration13&ndash14" />
[[File:Ravenscraig_Castle_01.jpg|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ravenscraig_Castle_01.jpg]]
城鎮的東邊坐落著雷文斯基格城堡遺址，這座城堡坐落在一片的岩石海岬上，海岬延伸至[[福斯湾|福斯灣]]。<ref name="Omand149">Omand 2000, p.149.</ref>1460年，苏格兰國王[[詹姆斯二世_(苏格兰)|詹姆斯二世]]為{{Link-en|格德司的瑪麗|Mary of Gueldres}}修建這座城堡。城堡也保衛包括戴薩一帶的福斯河上游地區。它亦保護了柯科迪海港免受海盜和英格蘭人的攻擊。<ref name="Torrie and Coleman63–64" /><ref name="Omand149" />雷文斯基格城堡建有巨大的城牆、放置火槍的射擊孔和岩石壕溝，是英國最早有實質防禦功能和使用火砲防衛的城堡之一。<ref name="Walker and Ritchie117">Walker and Ritchie 1996, p.117.</ref>詹姆斯二世去世後，雷文斯基格城堡的建造工程仍繼續進行，格德司的瑪麗亦居於此直至1463年去世。<ref name="Glen55">Glen 2007, p.55.</ref>1470年，苏格兰國王[[詹姆斯三世_(苏格兰)|詹姆斯三世]]將這座城堡和土地授予{{Link-en|奧克尼和凱斯內斯伯爵威廉·辛克禮|William Sinclair, 1st Earl of Caithness}}，以換取[[柯克沃尔|柯克和]]的城堡和授予{{Link-en|奧克尼伯爵|Earldom of Orkney}}爵位的權利。<ref name="Walker and Ritchie117" /><ref name="Glen55" />

==教育==
[[File:Balwearie_High_School,_Kirkcaldy.JPG|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Balwearie_High_School,_Kirkcaldy.JPG]]
1582年，在當地教會領袖大衛·史賓斯博士（David Spens） 的幫助下，柯科迪自治鎮學校（Kirkcaldy Burgh School） 得以成立， 校舍建於希爾街，是為該鎮的第一所學校。在到學校讀書之前，學生們大多在牧師家裡上課。<ref name="Remembered41">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2007, p.41.</ref>[[羅伯特·亞當|羅伯特·亞當]]和亞當·斯密亦曾於柯科迪自治鎮學校求學。<ref name="History and Celebration21">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, p.21.</ref>1843年柯科迪自治鎮學校被位於聖布賴斯杜大道（St. Brycedale Avenue）的柯科迪文法學校（Kirkcaldy Grammar School）取代。<ref name="History and Celebration21" /><ref name="Remembered44">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2007, p.44.</ref>一份寫於1872年的政府名單將柯科迪文法學校形容為一所「更高級」的學校。<ref name="Remembered44" />1893年，米高·乃因贊助學校興建新校舍。此外，鎮上還有不同種類的學校，包括女子學校和學徒學校。<ref name="Smith475–476">Smith 1952, pp.475–476.</ref>1872年通過的《蘇格蘭教育法令》規定孩童必須接受義務教育。<ref name="History and Celebration21" />

柯科迪有4所中學和11所小學，<ref name="Fife's primary schools">{{Cite web|title=A list of all primary schools in Fife|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?startRow=51&FUSEACTION=factype%2Edisplay&OBJECTID=BE6128F2%2D8785%2D11D6%2D9009%2D00508BDE7947&ORDERBY=location&SUBJECTID=xxx#anchor|accessdate=2014-02-28|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304072013/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?startRow=51&FUSEACTION=factype%2Edisplay&OBJECTID=BE6128F2%2D8785%2D11D6%2D9009%2D00508BDE7947&ORDERBY=location&SUBJECTID=xxx#anchor|archive-date=2014-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Fife's secondary schools">{{Cite web|title=A list of all secondary schools in Fife|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=factype.display&subjectid=xxx&objectid=BE6128F3-8785-11D6-9009-00508BDE7947&orderby=location|accessdate=2014-02-28|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304084014/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=factype.display&subjectid=xxx&objectid=BE6128F3-8785-11D6-9009-00508BDE7947&orderby=location|archive-date=2014-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>亦有一所私立學校和一所專為有學習需要學童開辦的學校。位於鄧尼克路的{{Link-en|柯科迪高中|Kirkcaldy High School}}是柯科迪最古老的高中，於1958年成立。<ref name="History and Celebration35–36">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, pp.35-36.</ref><ref name="KHS">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy High School profile|url=http://www.fife.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=2E7BE11F-3AC4-48CA-827BB61A6377A027#about|accessdate=2013-08-18|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302025142/http://www.fife.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=2E7BE11F-3AC4-48CA-827BB61A6377A027#about|archive-date=2014-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>柯科迪高中的學生大多來自柯科迪北部。{{Link-en|鮑華利高中|Balwearie High School}}於1964年成立時是一所初中，1972年升格為高中。<ref name="Glen116">Glen 2007, p.116.</ref><ref name="Balwearie HS">{{Cite web|title=Balwearie High School profile|url=http://www.fife.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=9678A744-536F-4D41-B4B85BD7453BEC6A|accessdate=2013-08-18|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302025046/http://www.fife.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=9678A744-536F-4D41-B4B85BD7453BEC6A|archive-date=2014-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>這所學校的學生大多來自柯科迪西部以及鄰近的景韓和本泰蘭。<ref name="Balwearie HS" />{{Link-en|威霍夫高中|Viewforth High School}}創立於1908年，最初也是一所初中，在1980年升級為高中。<ref name="Glen116" />政府已批准在柯科迪東部風車道運動場原址興建新中學的計劃<ref name="New KDY East HS approved">{{Cite news|author=Alexander|first=Michael|title='Massive' boost as council gives the school the green light|location=Dundee|publisher="The Courier" (Fife Edition)|page=4|date=2013-12-05}}</ref>，新中學校舍於2016年8月啟用。<ref name="Proposed new HS for Kdy East">{{Cite news|author=Wilson|first=Charlene|title=Viewforth views sought|location=Dundee|publisher="The Courier" (Fife Edition)|page=7|date=2013-05-16}}</ref><ref name="Kdy East HS">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy East Secondary School - Proposed Document|url=http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_TXKldyEastConsultationProposalJO140513.pdf|date=2013-05-17|format=PDF|publisher=Fife Council|pages=4–5|access-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225159/http://publications.1fife.org.uk/uploadfiles/publications/c64_TXKldyEastConsultationProposalJO140513.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>聖安德魯斯RC高中創立於1950年代末，是法夫的兩所[[天主教會|羅馬天主教]]中學之一。<ref name="Glen116" /><ref name="St Andrews">{{Cite web|title=St Andrews RC High School status|url=http://www.fife.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=97B6298C-418C-4F11-BCBE5F5909037A69|accessdate=2008-07-08|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060926002118/http://www.fife.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=97B6298C-418C-4F11-BCBE5F5909037A69|archive-date=2006-09-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

位於聖布賴斯杜大道，2013年8月由亞當史密斯學院、法夫學院和鄧弗姆林卡內基學院合併而成的的{{Link-en|法夫學院|Fife College}}為柯科迪居民提供持續教育。<ref name="Fife Regional College46">Fife College, "Think Fife College, Prospectus 2016-17", p.46.</ref><ref name="Colleges merge">{{Cite news|author=Alexander|first=Michael|title=Big Day as Colleges merge|location=Dundee|publisher="The Courier"|page=6|date=2013-08-01}}</ref>[[鄧迪大學|鄧迪大學]]亦於柯科迪開設一個專門的護理和助產學校。<ref name="Kdy campus">{{Cite web|title=Our Campuses|url=http://www.dundee.ac.uk/general/campusguide/ourcampuses.htm|accessdate=2011-09-20|publisher=The University of Dundee|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906022904/http://www.dundee.ac.uk/general/campusguide/ourcampuses.htm|archive-date=2011-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 公共服務 ==
法夫地方政府負責處理柯科迪鎮內的廢物，亦管理回收中心和廢物回收處。<ref name="recycling points in Kirkcaldy">{{Cite web|title=List of recycling points in Kirkcaldy|url=http://www.fifefire.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.list&CurrLetter=K|accessdate=2011-02-17|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722175210/http://www.fifefire.gov.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.list&CurrLetter=K|archive-date=2011-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>柯科迪的[[資源回收|回收]]站設有三色回收桶。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy east end shops say bin plans are rubbish!|url=https://www.fifetoday.co.uk/business/kirkcaldy-east-end-shops-say-bin-plans-are-rubbish-1-4237194|accessdate=2019-07-20|work=www.fifetoday.co.uk|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720111558/https://www.fifetoday.co.uk/business/kirkcaldy-east-end-shops-say-bin-plans-are-rubbish-1-4237194|archive-date=2019-07-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>無害廢物會被送往下梅維爾叢林（Lower Melville Wood）堆填區。<ref name="Landfill sites">{{Cite web|title=Landfill Sites in Fife|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/topics/index.cfm?fuseaction=page.display&p2sid=0B5AB7AD-9CE3-49C2-E2249C7B23835FF3&themeid=81E299FB-1BCF-4994-8C8A-233463B738F6|date=2011-06-22|publisher=Fife Council|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318152619/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/topics/index.cfm?fuseaction=page.display&p2sid=0B5AB7AD-9CE3-49C2-E2249C7B23835FF3&themeid=81E299FB-1BCF-4994-8C8A-233463B738F6|archivedate=2012-03-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

法夫國民保健署為柯科迪居民提供醫療保健服務，其總部設在希菲大廈（Hayfield House）。<ref name="NHS Fife Contacts">{{Cite web|title=NHS Fife - Contact Us|url=http://www.nhsfife.org/nhs/index.cfm?fuseaction=nhs.pagedisplay&p2sid=E8532DAC-5056-8C6F-C010EEB379DE6862&themeid=B62913A7-AEE9-0C0B-A51FC333AF909397|accessdate=2014-02-24|publisher=NHS Fife|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216213203/http://www.nhsfife.org/nhs/index.cfm?fuseaction=nhs.pagedisplay&p2sid=E8532DAC-5056-8C6F-C010EEB379DE6862&themeid=B62913A7-AEE9-0C0B-A51FC333AF909397|archive-date=2014-02-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Link-en|維多利亞醫院|Victoria Hospital (Kirkcaldy)}}位於市中心北部，是一間設有急症室和產科的醫院。一項耗資1.525億英鎊的擴建工程於2012年2月竣工，<ref name="GH&MS Newsletter3">{{Cite news|title=GH&MS (General Hospital & Maternity Services) Project Newsletter|issue=Issue 5|publisher=NHS Fife|location=Kirkcaldy|date=February 2011}}</ref>擴建面積達53萬平方英尺（4.9萬平方米），增設一個產房、兒童病房、十一個手術室和一個新的急診室。<ref name="GH&MS Newsletter3" /><ref name="Victoria Hospital extension">{{Cite web|title=New Wing, Victoria Hospital, Kirkcaldy|url=http://www.tatasteelconstruction.com/file_source/StaticFiles/Construction/Panels_and_profiles/case_studies/gallery_sheets/Victoria-Hospital-case-study.pdf|accessdate=2014-02-28|year=2012|format=PDF|publisher=Tata Steel|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924113313/http://www.tatasteelconstruction.com/file_source/StaticFiles/Construction/Panels_and_profiles/case_studies/gallery_sheets/Victoria-Hospital-case-study.pdf|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>維多利亞醫院{{Link-en|銘琪中心|Maggie's centres}}（Maggie's Centre）專門為癌症患者提供醫療服務。<ref name="Maggie's Fife">{{Cite web|title=Maggie's Cancer Care Centre, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom|url=http://www.designbuild-network.com/projects/maggies/|accessdate=2010-11-09|publisher=designbuild-network.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810032055/http://www.designbuild-network.com/projects/maggies/|archive-date=2011-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Glen285">Glen 2007, p.285.</ref>該中心是英國建築師[[薩哈·哈帝|扎哈·哈迪德]]設計的第一座建築。專為精神病患者和老年患者提供服務的惠文比醫院（Whyteman's Brae）也是柯科迪醫療系統一部分。<ref name="Whyteman's Brae">{{Cite web|title=Whyteman's Brae Hospital|url=http://www.nhsfife.org/nhs/index.cfm?fuseaction=nhs.facilitydisplay&p2sid=A59957D3-0443-899A-381D25E68EBEEDAE&themeid=E4689E2B-5056-8C6F-C0BF8FA7CD6A38D0|accessdate=2014-02-28|publisher=NHS Fife|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305003229/http://www.nhsfife.org/nhs/index.cfm?fuseaction=nhs.facilitydisplay&p2sid=A59957D3-0443-899A-381D25E68EBEEDAE&themeid=E4689E2B-5056-8C6F-C0BF8FA7CD6A38D0|archive-date=2014-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

蘇格蘭消防和救援局提供緊急消防和救援服務，消防總局設於鄧尼克路。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Fire Station">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Fire Station|url=http://www.firescotland.gov.uk/your-area/east/local-stations/kirkcaldy.aspx|accessdate=2014-02-28|publisher=Scottish Fire and Rescue Service|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301005033/http://www.firescotland.gov.uk/your-area/east/local-stations/kirkcaldy.aspx|archive-date=2014-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>至於柯科迪的警務工作由蘇格蘭警方負責，警察總局設於聖布賴斯杜大道上。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Police Station">{{Cite web|title=Fife Police Offices|url=http://www.scotland.police.uk/police-stations/fife/kirkcaldy-police-office/|accessdate=2014-02-28|publisher=Police Scotland|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305020215/http://www.scotland.police.uk/police-stations/fife/kirkcaldy-police-office/|archive-date=2014-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 運輸 ==
A92公路西邊連接敦費蘭，北邊連接[[格倫羅西斯|格倫羅西斯]]和[[邓迪|邓迪]]。A910公路貫穿柯科迪西部和中部。A921公路連接A92公路，亦經過聖嘉麗街（St. Clair Street）和濱海中心，盡頭處位於本泰蘭的景韓和法夫西南部的[[阿伯杜爾|阿伯杜爾]]。B981公路貫穿柯科迪北部，與A92公路大致平行。B981公路亦連接A910和A921公路，經教堂平道和鄧尼克路到格拉頓。<ref name="Nicolson Maps7">Nicolson Maps 2002, p.7.</ref><ref name="Nicolson Maps32">Nicolson Maps 2002, p.32.</ref>A915公路連接柯科迪、聖安德魯斯和東北部的列文（Leven）。A955公路沿著海岸線從戴薩一直延伸到{{Link-en|東韋米斯|East Wemyss}}和{{Link-en|巴黑文|Buckhaven}}。<ref name="Nicolson Maps32" /><ref name="Nicolson Maps37–39">Nicolson Maps 2002, pp.37–39.</ref>

柯科迪巴士總站設於希爾廣場（Hill Square）和亨特街（Hunter Street）交界，<ref name="Kdy Bus Station">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Bus Station|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=06E24949-E7FE-C7EA-0997650E43AD0F81|date=2011-07-15|publisher=Fife Council|access-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719084145/https://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=06E24949-E7FE-C7EA-0997650E43AD0F81|archive-date=2019-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>毗鄰購物中心。{{Link-en|柯科迪火車站|Kirkcaldy railway station}}是{{Link-en|法夫環線|Fife Circle Line}}和[[東海岸主線|東海岸主線]]的車站，位於市中心西北方。<ref name="Kirkcaldy Station">{{Cite web|title=Kirkcaldy Railway Station Profile|url=http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=029616FA-349C-4E36-856A1D88BFEDBA0F|accessdate=2008-06-23|publisher=Fife Council|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609153047/http://www.fifedirect.org.uk/atoz/index.cfm?fuseaction=facility.display&facid=029616FA-349C-4E36-856A1D88BFEDBA0F|archive-date=2011-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>柯科迪火車站亦有火車以[[阿伯丁|鴨巴甸]]、[[延文禮士|延文禮士]]或[[倫敦國王十字車站|倫敦國王十字車站]]為終點站。<ref name="History and Celebration110">Kirkcaldy Civic Society 2005, p.110.</ref>此外，本泰蘭站和景韓站分別在柯科迪的南部和西部。最近柯科迪的國際機場是[[愛丁堡機場|愛丁堡機場]]，距離柯科迪26英里（42公里）遠。

